title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-8.4 - Expiration date

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-8.4 - Expiration date

State Regulations

Section
646-8.3
of this Subpart shall expire upon: (a) the promulgation of regulations by the commission relative to wastewater
discharges and stormwater management and the issuance of a further Subpart to
limit commercial development consistent with such regulations; or
(b) July 15, 1990, whichever occurs
first. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
